{{Refimprove|date=September 2014}} {{Infobox motorsport championship | name = CASCAR Super Series | logo = | image-size = | caption = | category = [[Stock car racing|Stock cars]] | country/region = [[Canada]] | inaugural = 1986 | folded = 2006 | drivers = | teams = | constructors = [[Chevrolet]]{{·}}[[Dodge]]{{·}}[[Ford Motor Company|Ford]] | tires = | champion driver = [[J. R. Fitzpatrick]] | champion team = | manufacturer = [[Chevrolet]] | website = | current_season = }}
The '''CASCAR Super Series''' was Canada's premier stock car touring division. It was sanctioned by [[CASCAR]]. The series ended after the 2006 season after [[NASCAR]] purchased CASCAR. NASCAR used the series as the basis for the [[NASCAR Canadian Tire Series]], and currently called the Nascar Pinty's Series.
