{{italic title}}
'''''Decoding the Past''''' (2005–2008) is a [[History (U.S. TV channel)|History Channel]] [[paranormal]] [[television series]] that "[[:wikt:decode|decode]]s" the [[past]] by looking for unusual,  and mysterious things written about throughout history that may give clues as to what will happen in the [[future]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Decoding the Past (review)|url=http://www.commonsensemedia.org/tv-reviews/decoding-the-past|publisher=Commonsensemedia|accessdate=7 April 2014}}</ref>

